    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "I am the parent of Stephen from Grade 4. My child is joining the school trip which is planned next month. I am writing this letter to show my interest to join the trip so that I can assist the school and look after my son as well.",
        "My child has a sinus problem and it requires an immediate action if he gets a sinus attack. My doctor has advised me that it would be great if I can be with him during the trip. So, I have decided to come along in order to take care of his health.",
        "Apart from helping Steve, I can can handle the food for the whole group. Additionally, I can help staff with other arrangements that are required during the trip.",
        "Furthermore, I would like to check the amount required to confirm my seat for the trip and the last date to submit my details.",
        "Thank you for your kind attention. I am looking forward to your reply.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Barry Richardson"
    ],
